<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_View_Helper_FormSelect uses in_array() to test if a value is supposed to be selected.  Unfortunately, this causes a problem if one of the options has a value of 0.  Any option with a value of 0 will be selected no matter what.  I'm attaching a patch that fixes the problem.</p>

